{"article_id":"JIA3is9hF5hj6er1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After sitting through hours of testimony","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"and reading through thousands of pages of documents ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"a grand jury decided","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"that there was not enough probable cause","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"to indict police officer Darren Wilson in the shooting death of Michael Brown , an unarmed 18-year-old .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Their decision , like the shooting","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that led up to all this ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"sparked violent protests overnight in Ferguson , Mo .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"`` The duty of the grand jury is to separate fact and fiction , ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"the prosecuting attorney , Robert McCulloch , said in a televised address Monday night .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"After weighing the evidence ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"the grand jury decided","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that Wilson acted within the limits of the lethal-force law .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"To issue an indictment ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"the jury needed at least 9 members","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to vote for it .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"In a rare move and in an attempt","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to allay concerns about bias ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"McCulloch made public the mountain of evidence","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"presented to the grand jury .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"We 're combing through the thousands of pages","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"- including testimony from Wilson and many witnesses -","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"and throughout the day , we 'll update this post with the pieces","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"that help explain","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"how the jury reached its decision .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Leading up to this decision ,","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"witness testimony has been hotly debated","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"- so much so that the symbol of this story has become protesters","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"raising their hands ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"symbolically telling police ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"`` Hands up , do n't shoot . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"We have documents of dozens of witness interviews .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"If you listened to McCulloch last night ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"much of this jury 's decision came down to whether Brown was charging Wilson","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"or surrendering","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"or running away .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"As we 've detailed in another post ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"it 's really complicated .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Some witnesses say","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Wilson started shooting","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"after he got out of the car ;","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"some say","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"he started shooting inside the car .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Some say","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Brown was very clearly surrendering ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"others say","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"it did n't look like he had been hit at all .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Perhaps the simplest way","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"to explain all of this","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"is to take a close look at Witness 14 .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Without a doubt , Witness 14 is sympathetic to Brown","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and , in fact , had run into him at least once in the past .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` [ Brown ] was to me ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"and I 'm going to say it ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"he was executed , ''","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"the witness said .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"`` [ Wilson ] had made up his mind","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he was going to kill him . ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"That was the witness ' conclusion","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"as Brown was shot ,","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"he was surrendering ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"he had his hands up .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"That 's what the witness told local authorities .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"when the feds interviewed Witness 14","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"and drilled down on the details ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"the witness ' assumptions became less clear .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Were Brown 's hands a sign of surrender ?","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Or was he checking his injuries ?","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Were his palms facing the officer","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"or facing Brown ?","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"The witness eventually says :","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"`` He was defenseless ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"hands up ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"he was trying to stay on his feet","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and you could see","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"that his knees was beginning to buckle","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"and he was going down . ''","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"But the investigator eventually gets to a very important point .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"He leads the witness to say","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that Brown was moving toward Officer Wilson ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"who was screaming ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"`` Stop , ''","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"as he fired his weapon :","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Wilson 's testimony to the grand jury presents the image of an officer","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"who was scared for his life during the confrontation with the larger man","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"he says","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"was physically assaulting him .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"One excerpt :","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Wilson is 6 feet , 4 inches tall","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and weighs about 210 pounds .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Brown was an inch taller","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"and weighed about 290 pounds .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"The officer said","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Brown and his associate , Dorian Johnson , were walking in the middle of the street ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"preventing normal traffic from passing .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"he told them to move to the sidewalk ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and after a brief exchange Brown used a vulgarity at him .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Wilson said","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"he called for backup","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"and tried open the door of his police car .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Brown ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"slammed the door shut .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"They struggled","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"and Brown hit him in the face twice ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Wilson said .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"he thought ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"`` What do I do","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"to not get beaten inside my car ? ''","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Wilson said","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"he had considered using Mace , his baton and his flashlight","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"before drawing his gun","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"and telling Brown ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"`` Get back","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"or I 'm going to shoot you . ''","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"Brown then grabbed his gun ,","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Wilson said ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"and twisted it","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"and dug it down into the officer 's hip .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"The officer said","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"he feared","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"he would die","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"if Brown got hold of the gun .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"he managed to raise the gun","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"and fired twice .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"It just clicked .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"But the third time , the gun went off ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"startling both men .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"That 's when ,","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"Wilson said ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"Brown looked up at him","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"`` and had the most intense aggressive face .","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"The only way","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"I can describe it ,","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"it looks like a demon ,","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"that 's how angry he looked .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"He comes back towards me again","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"with his hands up . ''","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"Wilson said","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"he tried firing again","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"but nothing happened .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"When he tried once more ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"it went off .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Brown then hit him again ,","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"The officer said","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"when he looked up ,","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Brown was running away .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"Wilson said","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"he got out of the car ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"called for backup","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"and began chasing Brown .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"Brown then stopped","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"and he did , too .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"he ordered Brown to get on the ground ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"but the 18-year-old did not .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"Brown made an `` aggravated sound ''","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"and ran back toward him .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"he warned Brown repeatedly to get on the ground ,","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"but","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"when he did not comply","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"the officer fired `` a series of shots . ''","depth":16},{"id":174,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":16},{"id":175,"text":"how many I shot ,","depth":16},{"id":176,"text":"I just know","depth":16},{"id":177,"text":"I shot it , ''","depth":16},{"id":178,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"Wilson then proceeded to explain his rationale","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"for why he chased Brown .","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"he wanted to keep Brown `` contained ''","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"until support arrived .","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"he thought","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"if he could buy 30 seconds of time ,","depth":16},{"id":188,"text":"until other officers arrived ,","depth":16},{"id":189,"text":"they could `` make the arrest ,","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"nothing happens ,","depth":17},{"id":191,"text":"we are all good . ''","depth":17},{"id":192,"text":"One really important part of this case is of course the physical evidence .","depth":5},{"id":193,"text":"We 've gone into more details in a separate post .","depth":5},{"id":194,"text":"There are two findings of major importance :","depth":5},{"id":195,"text":"First , the autopsy found","depth":7},{"id":196,"text":"that Michael Brown was never shot in the back ,","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"as some early witnesses claimed .","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"Second , they found Brown 's blood inside the police car and on Wilson 's gun .","depth":7},{"id":199,"text":"This implies","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"that there was close-range contact","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"as Wilson alleges .","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"We 've also posted the photographs","depth":6},{"id":203,"text":"taken of Wilson on the day of the confrontation .","depth":6},{"id":204,"text":"Doctors diagnosed him with a bruise .","depth":5},{"id":205,"text":"That seems to cast some doubt on Wilson 's testimony about the intensity of the confrontation .","depth":4},{"id":206,"text":"We 've uploaded most of the documents","depth":4},{"id":207,"text":"we received from prosecutors .","depth":4},{"id":208,"text":"We invite you to look through them","depth":4},{"id":209,"text":"and tip us off to anything","depth":5},{"id":210,"text":"you find interesting in the comments .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":421,"left":402,"right":420,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":402,"left":235,"right":401,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":230,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":226,"right":229,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":220,"right":225,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":218,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":215,"right":217,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":212,"right":214,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":2,"right":213,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":213,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":216,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":222,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":10,"right":221,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":221,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity